{
  "stem": "10572.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father said, well you know, we don't have any chance until-- he said, get across the green border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, there will be war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "War will be soon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had some information that we didn't have yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know, in these kind of manifestations of decency among-- also kept us-- kept us going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they were really-- the-- the average citizen I think was frightened by all this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, as an indication and as a symbol of some of the things that happened, there was a man and a woman who lived in a little house who were in charge of the parks, a park worker, [NON-ENGLISH] Heineke.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day-- and my parents couldn't go to the grocery anymore to buy butter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, there was at night, there was the doorbell rang.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother went to the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a package-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --with a pound of butter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] So-- which is probably one of the reasons that when people judge and condemn people in general terms and say 'the Germans' or 'the Jews,' that is an injustice that I have learned through this whole period should not exist.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, because of what had happened during Kristallnacht, some positive forces came into effect.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we heard about it, that the Archbishop of Canterbury, Cosmo Long, had been convinced by a classmate of his from Goettingen University, Professor James Franck, Nobel Prize winner, who had convinced him in order to save 5,000 young Jews to convince the British government to start a camp.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Lord Kitchener Camp came into existence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was in England.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
